title: Gutterball 2
description:
The most realistic 3D bowling game is back! Five brand new alleys, 25 new eye-catching balls, tricky computer opponents, more modes and the most realistic physics to date. Check out the rebirth of the original 3D bowling game!

This game is from 2004, works great if you're drunk and have nothing better to do.

Requirements:
700MHz Pentium or equivalent,
works ok with 1 gig ram, works better with more
Operating Systems: 
Windows 98 
Windows ME 
Windows 2000 
Windows XP
Windows Vista
Windows 7
*in wine there is a problem with opengl, directx is needed
*no compatibility issues with 64 bit
